          "stem": "The document analysis agent discovers that two credible sources contain directly conflicting statistics on a key metric: one government report states 40% growth while an industry analysis states 12% growth. Both sources appear legitimate and the discrepancy could significantly affect the research conclusions. What's the most effective way for the document analysis agent to handle this?",
