          "stem": "You've asked Claude Code to implement a function that transforms API responses into a normalized internal format. After two iterations, the output structure still doesn't match expectations—some fields are nested differently and timestamps aren't formatted correctly. You've been describing the requirements in prose, but Claude seems to interpret them differently each time. What's the most effective approach for the next iteration?",
