          "stem": "Your team's CLAUDE.md file has grown to over 500 lines, mixing TypeScript conventions, testing guidelines, API patterns, and deployment procedures. Developers find it difficult to locate and update relevant sections. What approach does Claude Code support for organizing project-level instructions into focused, topic-specific modules?",
